  Sou2-lo5-bun5 in3 kong2, "Goa2 put-chi2 iu-bun7 ka-ki7 e5 tang7 choe7; goa2 e5 choe7-ok koan3-boan2, kiaN-1iau2 Siong7-te3 m7 sia3-bian2 goa2. "bok8-su kong2, “Li2 e5 choe7 sui-jian5 tang7, na7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 un-tian2 koh khah toa7.” Sou2-lo5-bun5 koh kong2, “KiaN-liau2 Siong7-te3 in-ui7 goa2 e5 tang7 choe7, m7 kheng2 si-un lin5-bin2 goa2." Bok8-su in3 kong2, "Na7- si7 li2 ko2-jian5 kian-sim sin3 Ia5-sou, goa2 chiu7 chiau3 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7 lai5 chi2-si7, hou7 li2 chai, li2 e5 choe7 i2-keng sia3-bian2 lah; koh li2 na7 hoaN-hi2, goa2 chiu7 thoe3 li2 ki5-to2 Siong7-te3." Sou2-lo5-bun5 kong2, "Che si7 goa2 e5 sim sou2 goan7." 
